OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779801070
OL,3,CSunderland return to European football
OL,4,Cafter 52 year wait
OL,6,FSunderland completed their Premier
OL,7,FLeague return in style after a 2-1 win
OL,8,Fover Chelsea confirmed their spot in
OL,9,Fthe Europa League next season.
OL,11,FTrai Hume sent the Black Cats ahead in
OL,12,Fthe 25th minute with a bottom-corner
OL,13,Ffinish and they doubled their
OL,14,Fadvantage five minutes after the
OL,15,Frestart through Malo Gusto's own goal
OL,16,Fin a chaotic start to the second half.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
