OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779801070
OL,3,CSunderland return to European football
OL,4,Cafter 52 year wait
OL,6,FCole Palmer pulled one back for
OL,7,FChelsea in the 56th minute, but just
OL,8,Fsix minutes later the Blues were
OL,9,Freduced to 10 when Wesley Fofana
OL,10,Fpicked up a second yellow card.
OL,12,FVictory combined with results
OL,13,Felsewhere cemented Sunderland's place
OL,14,Fin Europe next season, capping off a
OL,15,Fsensational top-flight return for the
OL,16,Fclub, who earned promotion exactly one
OL,17,Fyear ago to the day after beating
OL,18,FSheffield United in the Championship
OL,19,Fplay-off final at Wembley.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
